{"tid":1561013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵據報或取消中秋節通宵列車服務 九巴新巴及城巴相繼發稿加強當晚服務","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:51:08.000Z","uid":212626,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a64ffdfb7e20425095721ef555d353fcbfbbbd","tid":1561013,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"本周五(9月13日)便是中秋節，有報道指港鐵基於安全考慮，或不提供通宵列車服務，只會延長服務時間。港鐵回應傳媒查詢時未有否定相關報道，只稱有消息會公布。<br />\n<br />\n為方便市民出行、歡度佳節，港鐵以往每年逢農曆年三十晚、中秋節、平安夜及大除夕，多條港鐵路線都會通宵行駛；惟據《南華早報》報道，港鐵因近日多個車站被破壞，今日(11日)下午跟包括運輸及房屋局等政府官員會面後，擬取消中秋節當晚的通宵服務，只會延長部分路線的服務時間，以免人群在車站聚集；而鐵路工會聯合會今早亦已跟港鐵車務總監劉天成見面，擔心中秋節多個公眾活動或影響列車及車站運作，要求取消通宵服務，劉天成則回應工會指會跟政府及警方商討。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回應傳媒查詢時稱，有消息時會公布。<br />\n<br />\n報道亦引述政府官員將會安排其他交通服務接載市民，而九巴、新巴及城巴今日亦先後發新聞稿加強中秋節當晚的巴士服務；其中九巴指，將於中秋節當日9月13日(星期五)至翌日9月14日(星期六) 特別增強47條巴士路線服務，包括加密班次及開辦特別路線；而新巴及城巴亦稱，會增設特別路線，以及加強多條路線的班次，包括6、6X、260、307、619、681、780、788、789、930、930X、962B、962X、967、969、982X、N118、N171及N619，而其他通宵路線亦會因應情況加強服務。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2449558/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2449558%2F&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=36a462b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2449558/</a>"},{"pid":"3775c844b5a6cc6e903dbd7a836f2fab2c1bc99b","tid":1561013,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c2d82eb18923b26bcb4b6b45d5d1b13da5832968","tid":1561013,"uid":9548,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"巴士公司發達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb0a2525f648129208f7da67bb1cea8f0ae4e5c","tid":1561013,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5757e664b647eb38b0046a69467f2d56ec600c74","tid":1561013,"uid":60924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c2d82eb18923b26bcb4b6b45d5d1b13da5832968","tid":1561013,"uid":9548,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"巴士公司發達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"繼機場巴後另一發達日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cb182ccefb2aa42f6395a46010c89dcee9b96a","tid":1561013,"uid":222392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"執撚左佢啦屌！"},{"pid":"9554c369d6b30c4603642af442c18bb344548dd8","tid":1561013,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 全球齊篤灰2.0 向WhatsApp篤灰 #wtsappforhk #standwithhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560141</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b9d8274d4cb499284ce7e1faae492f7a972d9a3","tid":1561013,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a171b78a2549ec3bd